abandoned Oedipus

245
00:14:05,833 --> 00:14:09,375
in the forest when he
was still just a child.

246
00:14:09,458 --> 00:14:12,833
However, Oedipus survived
and grew into an adult.

247
00:14:12,916 --> 00:14:14,666
The Oracle was right,
and one day,

248
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,625
Oedipus did end up
killing Laius.

249
00:14:16,708 --> 00:14:21,333
Of course, at the time, he did
not know Laius was his father.

250
00:14:21,416 --> 00:14:24,250
[LISA] Afterwards, Oedipus
married the king's wife.

251
00:14:24,333 --> 00:14:27,166
But Queen Jocasta
was his mother.

252
00:14:29,208 --> 00:14:31,875
[LISA] When Oedipus
discovered the truth,

253
