and in order to punish himself,

256
00:14:41,541 --> 00:14:45,875
he gouged out his eyes,
making himself blind.

257
00:14:49,583 --> 00:14:50,458
[TWELVE]
Whatcha readin'?

258
00:14:50,541 --> 00:14:53,416
[LISA gasps]
Oh, I-- n-nothing.

259
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,916
Hm.

260
00:15:00,041 --> 00:15:04,291
[LISA] Um, if you don't mind
me asking, why are you here?

261
00:15:04,375 --> 00:15:07,333
I understand if
you're keeping tabs.

262
00:15:07,416 --> 00:15:09,333
It makes perfect sense.

263
00:15:09,416 --> 00:15:11,583
--You wanna learn a fun trick?
--[LISA] Huh?

264
00:15:11,666 --> 00:15:13,583
