It's the fresh maker cola!

269
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,750
[LISA]
Hey! Hold on a sec!

270
00:15:32,708 --> 00:15:40,166
[LISA panting]

271
00:15:40,250 --> 00:15:42,416
[KURAHASHI] Oedipus went to
visit the country of his father,

272
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:46,000
whom he had killed.
He was confronted there.

273
00:15:46,083 --> 00:15:49,333
A monster appeared
and blocked his way.

274
00:15:49,416 --> 00:15:50,416
[KURAHASHI]
The Sphinx asked riddles

275
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,041
