level of a beast, so to speak.

341
00:18:31,458 --> 00:18:32,750
That makes four.

342
00:18:32,833 --> 00:18:34,625
In the end, he gouged
out his own eyes,

343
00:18:34,708 --> 00:18:37,375
blinding himself.
He needed a cane to walk.

344
00:18:37,458 --> 00:18:39,666
So, three legs.

345
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:42,458
[LISA panting]

346
00:18:42,541 --> 00:18:44,041
[YOUNG MAN 2A]
Ah! Watch it!

347
00:18:44,125 --> 00:18:46,000
[LISA]
I'm sorry!

348
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:58,041
[LISA panting]

349
00:18:58,125 --> 00:19:01,416
