360
00:19:25,916 --> 00:19:27,750
Roppongi Station!

361
00:19:32,458 --> 00:19:41,083
[phone ringing]

362
00:19:41,166 --> 00:19:43,250
[TWELVE]
Nothing personal.

363
00:19:43,333 --> 00:19:46,750
But one false move,
and I'll have to kill ya.

364
00:19:46,833 --> 00:19:49,375
[LISA gasps]

365
00:19:49,458 --> 00:19:51,708
