372
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:20,375
[HAMURA]
Director!

373
00:20:20,458 --> 00:20:22,541
There was an explosion
at Roppongi Station!

374
00:20:22,625 --> 00:20:25,333
We should take this as a direct
challenge to the police force!

375
00:20:25,416 --> 00:20:26,500
[OKANO]
Hamura!

376
00:20:26,583 --> 00:20:28,208
Head to Roppongi immediately!

377
00:20:28,291 --> 00:20:29,625
[HAMURA]
Yes, sir!

378
00:20:29,708 --> 00:20:32,041
Shibazaki, understand
what I am about

379
