the government office.

389
00:20:55,833 --> 00:20:59,083
[SHIBAZAKI gasps]
Don't tell me.

390
00:20:59,166 --> 00:21:00,375
[KURAHASHI]
That's right.

391
00:21:00,458 --> 00:21:02,541
I think these guys
have every intention

